Changelog of Textbase Mailer 'Mave'

Version 2.99
	* Refine for ruby 2.0.
	* Add wiki edit function.

Version 2.98
	* Add web mail viewer 'Maverick'.
	* Add incremental search functions with romanized japanese stroke.
	* Add QDBM support for meta data store of mail.
	* Add legacy encoding mode for filename of attachment.
	* Add import address book function from ldap server.

Version 2.97
	* Add clip(quote) and tagjump function.
	* Add full-text search function for mail by external engine.
	* Add execute shell command and import result function.
	* Add execute present and postsend script function.(For prevent to forget to attach to mail)

Version 2.96
	* Add extract/enclose attachment files function.(Supprt RFC 2231 extensions)
	* Add ssl/tls protocol support.(Send/Receive Gmail account)
	* Correct permissions of related files.

Version 2.95
	* Add send mail function.
	* Add address book function.
	* Add filter and distribute mail function.
	* Add import mail function.
	* Add mail viewer(full screen) function.

Version 2.94
	* Add mail move, copy and delete functions.
	* Add arrange functions of mail thread relations.

Version 2.93
	* Add incremental search functions for summary or preview view.
	* Add move into the folder function by shortcut key.

Version 2.92
	* Add folder functions.

Version 2.91
	* Add message edit functions.

Version 2.90
	* Initial commit.
	* It can only fetch and explore mails.

[EOF]
